More from topic modeling on the (mostly) collected works of Marx and Engels. This time, the model has been expanded from 35 to 50 topics across 70 documents. It's remarkable how many disciplines they drew on to develop the scientific socialist method. #Marxism #RStats https://t.co/H3Tb75XR6t

Topic modeling with the collected works of Marx/Engels has been so much fun that I wrote an #Rstats function to scrape over 7000 public domain documents from dozens of authors from the Marxist Internet Archive. This should be pretty interesting.

And every time, I am wrong. Every. Time. #datajournalism #RStats

x is  25  and y is  5

because `|>` passes the value to function as the first argument.
